reviewText:
ELEMENTARY ALL OVER AGAIN, I LOVE IT
I CAN WATCH THIS OVER AND OVER AND OVER AGAIN
NEEDS TO RETURN TO TV

If you have looked at the episode 1 minidisc you probably already know what I'm gonna say, but I'm gonna say it again. This item is great for people who are collecting Invader Zim merchandise like me, but not if you are looking for a great place to buy the episodes, because theses discs only have 1 episode on them. I would recommend using Amazon Instant Video to buy the DvD's.
